{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"matrix()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>CSS 函数 <code>matrix()</code> 指定了一个由指定的 6 个值组成的 2D 变换矩阵。这种矩阵的常量值是隐含的，而不是由参数传递的；其他的参数是以列优先的顺序描述的。</p>\n<p><code>matrix(a, b, c, d, tx, ty)</code> 是 <code>matrix3d(a, b, 0, 0, c, d, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, tx, ty, 0, 1)</code> 的简写。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 直到 Firefox 16, Gecko 才接受对于 <strong>tx</strong> 和 <strong>ty</strong> 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> 值。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">matrix(a, b, c, d, tx, ty)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数值","title":"参数值","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"a\"><em>a</em> <em>b</em> <em>c</em> <em>d</em></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>描述线性变换的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/number\"><code>&lt;number&gt;</code></a> 。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tx\"><em>tx</em> <em>ty</em></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>描述如何应用这个变换的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/number\"><code>&lt;number&gt;</code></a> 。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"col\">ℝ<sup>2 </sup>下的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%AC%9B%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">笛卡尔坐标</a></th>\n      <th scope=\"col\">ℝℙ<sup>2 </sup>下<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BD%90%E6%AC%A1%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">齐次坐标</a></th>\n      <th scope=\"col\">ℝ<sup>3</sup>下的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%AC%9B%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E7%B3%BB\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">笛卡尔坐标</a></th>\n      <th scope=\"col\">ℝℙ<sup>3</sup>下的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BD%90%E6%AC%A1%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">齐次坐标</a></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n        <math>\n          <mfenced>\n            <mtable>\n              <mtr>\n                <mtd>a</mtd>\n                <mtd>c</mtd>\n              </mtr>\n              <mtr>\n                <mtd>b</mtd>\n                <mtd>d</mtd>\n              </mtr>\n            </mtable>\n          </mfenced>\n        </math>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>\n          <math>\n            <mfenced>\n              <mtable>\n                <mtr>\n                  <mtd></mtd>\n                </mtr>\n              </mtable>\n            </mfenced>\n          </math><br>a c tx<br>b d ty<br>0 0 1\n        </p>\n      </td>\n      <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n        <math>\n          <mfenced>\n            <mtable>\n              <mtr>\n                <mtd></mtd>\n              </mtr>a c tx\n            </mtable>\n          </mfenced>\n        </math><br>b d ty<br>0 0 1\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd></mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </td>\n      <td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n        <math>\n          <mfenced>\n            <mtable>\n              <mtr>\n                <mtd>a</mtd>\n                <mtd>c</mtd>\n                <mtd>0</mtd>\n                <mtd>tx</mtd>\n              </mtr>\n              <mtr>\n                <mtd>b</mtd>\n                <mtd>d</mtd>\n                <mtd>0</mtd>\n                <mtd>ty</mtd>\n              </mtr>\n              <mtr>\n                <mtd>0</mtd>\n                <mtd>0</mtd>\n                <mtd>1</mtd>\n                <mtd>0</mtd>\n              </mtr>\n              <mtr>\n                <mtd>0</mtd>\n                <mtd>0</mtd>\n                <mtd>0</mtd>\n                <mtd>1</mtd>\n              </mtr>\n            </mtable>\n          </mfenced>\n        </math>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>[a b c d tx ty]</code></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>这些值表示以下函数：</p>\n<p>matrix( scaleX(), skewY(), skewX(), scaleY(), translateX(), translateY() )</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;div&gt;Normal&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div class=\"changed\"&gt;Changed&lt;/div&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">div {\n  width: 80px;\n  height: 80px;\n  background-color: skyblue;\n}\n\n.changed {\n  transform: matrix(1, 2, -1, 1, 80, 80);\n  background-color: pink;\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<p>请看英文版案例 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix#Result\" aria-current=\"page\">/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/matrix#Result</a></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-transforms/#funcdef-transform-matrix","title":"CSS Transforms Module Level 1"}],"query":"css.types.transform-function.matrix"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"参数值","id":"参数值"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"CSS 函数 matrix() 指定了一个由指定的 6 个值组成的 2D 变换矩阵。这种矩阵的常量值是隐含的，而不是由参数传递的；其他的参数是以列优先的顺序描述的。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"matrix()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"matrix()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/css/transform-function/matrix","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/css/transform-function/matrix/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com